    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'A hidden treasure tower rises above the kingdom. Ali, the young climber,
    must cross five dangerous floors, collect the tower gems, and unlock the final
    summit door before the ancient treasure is lost forever.


    Every level tests
    a different skill: timing, courage, careful jumps, and survival against ground
    and flying enemies. Collect more coins, finish faster, and die less to improve
    your record.


    Game Development subject: IT8101

    Supervised by Doctor
    Albaraa Janahi

    Course Coordinator: Haetham Alhadad

    Section 2, Year
    Semester 2, 2025-2026'
